      "text": "ありがとうございます、頑固なところがあるから\n素直に意見を聞き入れてもらえてホッとしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ I was relieved to hear that because you can be so stubborn.\nI'm glad you took my opinion to heart.",
